{"type": "article", "id": 9728, "title": "Valentino & Aston Martin 定制跑车", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-19T07:18:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606142317uC6Rw1Wc3HeEKsx9.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tValentino 最近和 Aston Martin 联合推出了一款定制跑车，把其标志性的迷彩图案涂满了整个车身。同时，在无处不在的铆钉元素也时时刻刻宣布着 Valentino 的气质。这款跑车出自 Maria Grazia Chiuri 和 Pierpaolo Piccioli 之手，系支持慈善工作设计。在 2015 年 “Cash &amp;Rocket on Tour” 的晚宴拍卖，所得收益捐给 Cash &amp;Rocket on Tour 所支持的慈善机构。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142314sAiLqrmH3p7aQWwB.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.70660147\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061423159WKiVpQM5mq0o3s7.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.70660147\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142315LcW8YyAP5gJnUeGC.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.70660147\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142316TL9i2xeyKfGDdQtq.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.70660147\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606142316zsS0xUAfXaIcPHuB.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.70660147\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}